Paper: hep-th/9605076

Date: 1996-05-10

Title: On a Order Reduction Theorem in the Lagrangian Formalism

Comments: 9 pages, LATEX, no figures; appear in Il Nuovo Cimento B

Journal-ref: Nuovo Cim. B111 (1996) 1439-1447

We provide a new proof of a important theorem in the Lagrangian formalismabout necessary and sufficient conditions for a second-order variational systemof equations to follow from a first-order Lagrangian.